# Input

```scss
$map:(key:(#d82d2d,#666),other-key:(#52bf4a,#fff),);


```


# Formatted

```scss
$map: (
	key: (
		#d82d2d,
		#666,
	),
	other-key: (
		#52bf4a,
		#fff,
	),
);

```
